wiki.content:
It is the birth of Jack Black's need for metal! Also, it brings forth Meatloaf and also Ronnie James Dio, an under-recognized rocker, and one of the gods of metal.   This is the opening song to The Pick of Destiny, a comedy/rock opera, one of the greatest rock and roll movies of all time.
 
 ... in memory of Ronnie James Dio 1942 - 2010 ...
